column3: The rdfs:Class that is the rdf:type of all entities in a class-based partition.
The total number of distinct classes in a void:Dataset.
A subset of a void:Dataset that contains only the entities of a certain rdfs:Class.
An RDF dump, partial or complete, of a void:Dataset.
The total number of distinct objects in a void:Dataset.
The total number of distinct subjects in a void:Dataset.
The total number of documents, for void:Datasets that are published as a set of individual RDF documents.
The total number of entities that are described in a void:Dataset.
An example entity that is representative for the entities described in a void:Dataset.
A void:TechnicalFeature supported by a void:Datset.
Points to the void:Dataset that a document is a part of.
Specifies the RDF property of the triples in a void:Linkset.
The void:Dataset that contains the resources in the object position of a void:Linkset's triples.
An OpenSearch description document for a free-text search service over a void:Dataset.
The total number of distinct properties in a void:Dataset.
The rdf:Property that is the predicate of all triples in a property-based partition.
A subset of a void:Dataset that contains only the triples of a certain rdf:Property.
A top concept or entry point for a void:Dataset that is structured in a tree-like fashion.
A SPARQL protocol endpoint that allows SPARQL query access to a void:Dataset.
The void:Dataset that contains the resources in the subject position of this void:Linkset's triples.
A void:Dataset that is part of another void:Dataset.
One of the two void:Datasets connected by this void:Linkset.
The total number of triples contained in a void:Dataset.
A protocol endpoint for simple URI lookups for a void:Dataset.
A regular expression that matches the URIs of a void:Dataset's entities.
A URI that is a common string prefix of all the entity URIs in a void:Datset.
A vocabulary or owl:Ontology whose classes or properties are used in a void:Dataset.
